Description: Vera Bradley's Tall Zip Tote was introduced as a Book Bag, an alternative to a crossbody messenger bag or an over-the-back backpack which can be hard on the back. The straps are long enough to carry this like a purse and the main zipper compartment is deep enough to carry quite a few large hardcovers or binders. There are two front magnetic flap pockets to put your supplies in and one zipper compartment in the back to store peripherals or your daytimer. This is a cute bag, one of Vera's most popular.
